ote>桂林都好似唔差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/AB/AF/wKgBpVWolOmASIhlAAEaMKdhcSw07.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21690x370r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21690x370%2Fquality%2F100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc4-q.mafengwo.net%2Fs8%2FM00%2FAB%2FAF%2FwKgBpVWolOmASIhlAAEaMKdhcSw07.jpeg%3FimageMogr2%252Fthumbnail%252F%2521690x370r%252Fgravity%252FCenter%252Fcrop%252F%2521690x370%252Fquality%252F100&h=336b5d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSVBGRzPTRe32a1XAvX-L4TwLnV00CJI5jtC6N3hKw-GcvnJrOm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSVBGRzPTRe32a1XAvX-L4TwLnV00CJI5jtC6N3hKw-GcvnJrOm&h=7cd6d9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.ngaynay.vn/w500/Uploaded/oldavatars2/Uploaded/maiphuong/2015_08_06/ngaynayquelamtrungquocduhoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.ngaynay.vn%2Fw500%2FUploaded%2Foldavatars2%2FUploaded%2Fmaiphuong%2F2015_08_06%2Fngaynayquelamtrungquocduhoc.png&h=e1a4f743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.yaoquna.com/upload/2017/04/18/55f0bad08b4e8978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yaoquna.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F55f0bad08b4e8978.jpg&h=f3e76c8c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇巴打去過？<br />\nBudget 幾多度？<br />\n好唔好玩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去過一次，洗費好平，二千都夠做，酒店100人仔一晚質素唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲山同梯田係幾靚，但環境麻麻，d當地團要好早起身，勁多野食，</blockquote><br />\n未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成條食街，雖然全部都黑心食用，但好平又好食！<br />\n結論：輕鬆下ok但唔好期望太高"},{"pid":"eaf23df2f7c2e6558e0dbf8e93e4aafbb1b52e56","tid":274801,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:32:04.000Z","msg":"去昆明麗江"},{"pid":"7393cf0fdbae7a929d995e79b62d2860f1699d7d","tid":274801,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n<br />\n雲南、西藏、四川...中國人西南西北都好值得去<br />\n沿海城市、重點市、直轄市、首都，請都唔好去<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n<br />\nD幾多星國家級旅遊景點，雖然係亂黎，但都有參考價值，4星以下都係廢，4星十個有九個廢，5星都要考慮下<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n<br />\n去西南西北頂得順既都建議你坐火車，會睇多好多野<br />\n<br />\n第四<br />\n<br />\nLocal tour十個有七個劏客，街邊拉客大媽一個都唔好理<br />\n<br />\n第五<br />\n<br />\n二千蚊係去下廣西桂林咁上下，不過桂林都已經唔係以前讀書講到山水甲天下咁正"},{"pid":"9cc50d1a6abfb1caea8c500d8c270b63c20915a2","tid":274801,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張家界<br />\n桂林<br />\n長白山<br />\n九寨溝<br />\n西藏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張家界，2k唔夠<br />\n桂林，已變人工災難，2k都唔多夠<br />\n長白山， 機票都去左千幾了<br />\n九寨溝，捱巴士火車免強夠<br />\n西藏，當睇唔到！ <br />\n<br />\n2k buget係廣東hea遊就免強"},{"pid":"c97e2c320aac10015f31d61ae1cfaee35405eb0c","tid":274801,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>桂林都好似唔差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/AB/AF/wKgBpVWolOmASIhlAAEaMKdhcSw07.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21690x370r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21690x370%2Fquality%2F100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc4-q.mafengwo.net%2Fs8%2FM00%2FAB%2FAF%2FwKgBpVWolOmASIhlAAEaMKdhcSw07.jpeg%3FimageMogr2%252Fthumbnail%252F%2521690x370r%252Fgravity%252FCenter%252Fcrop%252F%2521690x370%252Fquality%252F100&h=336b5d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSVBGRzPTRe32a1XAvX-L4TwLnV00CJI5jtC6N3hKw-GcvnJrOm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSVBGRzPTRe32a1XAvX-L4TwLnV00CJI5jtC6N3hKw-GcvnJrOm&h=7cd6d9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.ngaynay.vn/w500/Uploaded/oldavatars2/Uploaded/maiphuong/2015_08_06/ngaynayquelamtrungquocduhoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.ngaynay.vn%2Fw500%2FUploaded%2Foldavatars2%2FUploaded%2Fmaiphuong%2F2015_08_06%2Fngaynayquelamtrungquocduhoc.png&h=e1a4f743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.yaoquna.com/upload/2017/04/18/55f0bad08b4e8978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yaoquna.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F55f0bad08b4e8978.jpg&h=f3e76c8c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪信。。。上年先去完，自駕遊。"},{"pid":"051bf5605432c9727fc32bc4a1d229a87e365fb1","tid":274801,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>七年前去九寨溝好靚</blockquote><br />\n岩岩search左啲圖<br />\n好似好正咁，係我鍾意個類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.peacetour.com.tw/eWeb_peacetour/IMGDB/000001/000130/00003178.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.peacetour.com.tw%2FeWeb_peacetour%2FIMGDB%2F000001%2F000130%2F00003178.JPG&h=39268522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.liontravel.com/album_photo/1453/previews-med/1453-760801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.liontravel.com%2Falbum_photo%2F1453%2Fpreviews-med%2F1453-760801.jpg&h=a0f0e7c3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真係有咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲十月份入秋最靚既相，你幾時去先？七、八月既話<br />\n<br />\n打個五折就差唔多。"},{"pid":"77d6b3279f814f63cff7da79801ce0eb7062d0d8","tid":274801,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"大陸主要係機票同景點門票較大使費（如果有學生證記得帶埋去，有半價），食同住都可以好平。得2-3000可以上網睇下有冇平機票先決定去邊度。"},{"pid":"d8f1fdc3ab0cf0e9463c6e6e2f7a89b0fb248cc8","tid":274801,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸主要係機票同景點門票較大使費（如果有學生證記得帶埋去，有半價），食同住都可以好平。得2-3000可以上網睇下有冇平機票先決定去邊度。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果 長少少 去既話<br />\n最好住青旅 識下d local<br />\n同佢地一齊拼車 食飯 平好多<br />\n始終佢地一定熟路過你<br />\n<br />\n宜家大陸人開始有錢 出晒黎玩<br />\n旅遊地方 已經唔係你想像咁平<br />\n早去早享受<br />\n<br />\n好似 色達 牛背山 呢d過多幾年已經唔同"},{"pid":"3b260d1038ca7070b36b06d2118e660f0e5507db","tid":274801,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"3k係人仔定港紙先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去桂林唔錯，坐鳩鐵去來回444蚊<br />\n桂林玩一日再坐大巴去陽朔<br />\n遊十里畫廊同西街。響陽朔又可以坐返竹划去桂林<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df49c7f6ca2532c08d86e3136041ad97ced50cb3","tid":274801,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"去青海環線<br />\n應該用左6 7000"},{"pid":"9541f73bb4f7cf1f6d28002b8e7409d348b408b5","tid":274801,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f2a10cd151bcf385185419af6d27c739c6231df","tid":274801,"uid":85063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"[quote]如果想去大陸旅遊，筆直大約2000以內<br />\n<br />\n個人喜好，鍾意啲自然風景、歷史文物、藝術建築、山海湖泊<br />\n<br />\n應該去邊度好？<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲幫幫手比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote<br />\n<br />\n返廣東先得wor"},{"pid":"e107db9076a3d50538e141b705d101c6aab88a5f","tid":274801,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"九寨溝真係好似相咁靚 上年去過<br />\n不過仲未寄行程食宿交通 門票都3,4百人仔<br />\n2000真係出唔到廣東省"},{"pid":"b1a5ba6a85974e29053864505be6492eced792d3","tid":274801,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九寨溝真係好似相咁靚 上年去過<br />\n不過仲未寄行程食宿交通 門票都3,4百人仔<br />\n2000真係出唔到廣東省</blockquote><br />\n九寨溝唔好話2000, 4000都忟水啦.<br />\n上網CHECK 下, 深圳飛成都已經要大約1500人仔.圍返港紙都差唔多1700. <br />\n2000-3000 , 又唔洗一定留晌廣東既.<br />\n2000: 廣西, 福建,金門, 馬祖都仲夠.<br />\n3000: 海南,上海,杭州都OK"},{"pid":"6c9782c956c3ef520bd454bb0bac6526211b1413","tid":274801,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>九寨溝真係好似相咁靚 上年去過<br />\n不過仲未寄行程食宿交通 門票都3,4百人仔<br />\n2000真係出唔到廣東省</blockquote><br />\n九寨溝唔好話2000, 4000都忟水啦.<br />\n上網CHECK 下, 深圳飛成都已經要大約1500人仔.圍返港紙都差唔多1700. <br />\n2000-3000 , 又唔洗一定留晌廣東既.<br />\n2000: 廣西, 福建,金門, 馬祖都仲夠.<br />\n3000: 海南,上海,杭州都OK</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n火車上成都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d96347a78ebde2bbc276b14c5d5850857c8442b","tid":274801,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"桂林<br />\n張家界<br />\n九寨溝<br />\n都去過哂 如果樓主打算全部都去既話 九寨溝一定要放最後 因為靚太多<br />\n<br />\n九寨溝&gt;&gt;張家界&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;桂林<br />\n個人意見 不喜勿屌<br />\n<br />\n無追post 好似見到樓主budget 唔多<br />\n如果係咁 不如試下張家界"},{"pid":"0603b292c599122401c46484e5dd8cb806d649e4","tid":274801,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"2-3000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出唔到廣東省啦,<br />\n飛機都至少用你800-1500啦,除非UO飛昆明/寧波<br />\n<br />\n大陸最撚貴係入場費,食住都唔算貴<br />\n<br />\n3千蚊最多咪去到廣東,廣西,廈門...<br />\n或者來個快閃黃山都得,前提機票夠平<br />\n<br />\n張家界都唔得啦...貴到HIHI"},{"pid":"d48197a0b18607e99153f041c9d6651cf93eb404","tid":274801,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:34:48.000Z","msg":"另外九寨溝真心好撚靚,去完你以後對於呢D山山水水就全部都比唔上九寨溝,靚到仙境咁,好撚誇張,但一定要係10月中下旬去,最靚季節"},{"pid":"c3f29edd7dcbe3d608125463a30e8a66e87403a8","tid":274801,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外九寨溝真心好撚靚,去完你以後對於呢D山山水水就全部都比唔上九寨溝,靚到仙境咁,好撚誇張,但一定要係10月中下旬去,最靚季節</blockquote><br />\n九寨歸來不看水"},{"pid":"6b1b04e6c0ae1cb6e16cf4bdba88b3c2a138576e","tid":274801,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"貴州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj